Web application for mobile web version of the application

This is a Sinatra based application.

Using ruby 1.9.3

Make sure you have bundler installed (gem install bundler)
1. clone the project
2. run `bundle install`

3. If you haven't imported the www submodule yet, do the following
  3a. At the root of this project's directory, run `git submodule update --init`

4. run `rackup`

The application is now running, and can be accessed from a mobile web browser.
